   LEHIGH-ON-THE-RISE (Bethlehem, Pa.) _ So much for the persistent
perception of the Lehigh Valley of Pennsylvania as a place whose
time has come and gone. Drive through the area, visit its schools,
talk to its entrepreneurs and glimpse the billboard proclaiming
``Move over, Silicon Valley, here comes Lehigh Valley.'' While that
is an exaggeration, what is certain is that a high-tech phoenix has
slowly risen on the steel scrap heaps of Easton, Bethlehem and
Allentown _ the towns that make up the Lehigh Valley. By Claudia H.
Deutsch.
