   MARKETPLACE-DIVIDENDS (Undated) _ While the economy is doing
well, companies are growing more reluctant to increase their
dividends. In September, 117 companies announced dividend increases
_ 10 fewer than had raised their payouts a year earlier. It is the
15th consecutive month that dividend increases are down from a year
ago.
