   MEXICO-RATS (Zacatecas, Mexico) _ Luncheonette owners Joanna and
Catalina Herrera swear it has more healing powers than chicken
soup. Gerardo Luna, a state employee, says that when prepared as a
tea with anise and pepper, it can ``raise the dead.'' The secret?
Rat meat. By Richard Chacon. 725 words.
