<P>
   BRITAIN-WRECK _ LONDON _ Rescue workers clad in white plastic
coveralls entered the charred and mangled commuter rail car
Wednesday morning that officials fear may contain many more bodies
of people killed Tuesday in one of Britain's worst ever rail
disasters. Developing. (Roughton, Cox Bews Service).
</P>
