<P>
   BRADLEY _ Democrat Bill Bradley, who has shown surprising
strength against Vice President Gore, appears to have trumped Gore
in an area close to the vice president's heart: online fundraising.
Analysts say that the $650,000 Bradley has raised on his internet
site has shattered previous fundraising records for online
contributions. His success reflects both his clever on-line
strategy and the nature of his constituency. (Foskett, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 25'.
