<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-RUNAWAY-PRODUCTION-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
CONGRESSMEN ACCUSE CANADA OF LURING AWAY PRODUCTION
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY DAVE MCNARY  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES -- A coalition of eight Congressmen fired another
shot Wednesday at Canada over its efforts to lure Hollywood
productions north of the border.
</P>
<P>
   The group, led by Rep. Howard Berman, D-Mission Hills, is
