   &UR; AUTOWEB  &LR; _ Internet car seller Autoweb launched the first
consumer-to-consumer online auto action service on Wednesday.
Competitor Autobytel.com is expected to follow suit today. BY TOM
STEIN.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; GEOCAST  &LR; _ Silicon Valley startup Geocast soon will deliver
personalized data, graphics and full-screen, full-motion video to
PCs at eye-popping speeds with virtually no bandwidth constraints
and no download times. Geocast is funded by Kleiner Perkins
Caulfield &AMP; Byers, The Mayfield Fund and Institutional Venture
Partners _ the first time these three have hooked up to back the
same company. BY BENNY EVANGELISTA.
