</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GRAPHIC-FILES-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times News Service Macintosh
graphics files that moved Wednesday, 10/6/99. Included is the
corresponding story slug and the size. All graphics have been
posted on PressLink, NewsCom and the Wieck Photo Database.
</P>
<P>
   ISRAEL_Zone of Control map -- 1 x 2 1/4 -- ISRAEL-LEBANON
</P>
<P>
   RUSSIA_Omsk locator -- 1 x 2 1/4 -- RUSSIA-YELTSIN-FAMILY
</P>
<P>
   IRAQ_Incirlik Air Base map -- 1 x 2 1/4 -- IRAQ-U.S.
</P>
<P>
   NY-POVERTY_U.S. Compare -- 2 x 4 -- NY-POVERTY-STUDY
</P>
<P>
   HOME_Leaky valves.pdf -- 42p6 x 4 -- HOME-IMPROVEMENT
</P>
<P>
   MONSTER_Playground diag. -- 30p6 x 4 3/4 -- MONSTER-PLAYGROUND
</P>
<P>
   FBN_Pro rankings 10-7 -- 36p x 8 3/8 -- FBN-RANKINGS
